flowchart TD
    Start([Start Racer Registration]) --> Login[Racer logs in]
    Login --> Select[Selects a race]
    Select --> Check1{Is registration open?}
    Check1 -- No --> End1([End])
    Check1 -- Yes --> Check2{Is race full?}

    Check2 -- Yes --> End2([End])
    Check2 -- No --> Check3{Is race official?}

    Check3 -- No --> Check5{Does racer meet category for race?}
    Check3 -- Yes --> Check4{Does racer have a valid license?}

    Check4 -- Yes --> Check5
    Check4 -- No --> Buy[Prompt racer to buy a license]
    Buy --> Bought{Did racer purchase a license?}
    Bought -- No --> End3([End])
    Bought -- Yes --> Check5

    Check5 -- No --> End4([End])
    Check5 -- Yes --> Submit[Racer registers for race]
    Submit --> Save[Save race registration to database]
    Save --> Done([End])
